    "This review highlights the current status of the use of AI in pain assessment, including different techniques, advantages, limitations, and challenges, and provides data for future directions.",
    "METHODOLOGYA computer search was conducted including literature from PubMed, EMBASE, MEDLINE, Web of Science, Cochrane, and Google Scholar.",
    "Manual screening of references from relevant sites was also conducted, and additional references were added.",
    "The search strategy included articles that were published during the last 10 years (from January 2014 to January 2024).",
